I '''[[Santa]] María Mazzarello''' o '''Madre Mazzarello''' (Mayo 9, 1837 – Mayo 14, 1881) ing Italianang kayabe nang Don Boscong mitátag kareng [[Salesian Sisters of Don Bosco|Salesian Sisters]], a mayayaus muring "''salesianas''". I Madre Mazzarello, a lagyu nung nu ne mas kilala ning yatu, ing mumunang Superiora General ning kayang orden manibat [[29 Marzo]] ning [[1872]] angga king kayang maranun a pangamate anyang [[1881]]. Uling king kayang misnang pangasimpli ampo ing kayang pamiparikil (''dedication'') king kayang bye king pamitátag ning bersyong pambabai ning sistema ning pamisapul (''preventive system'') nang Don Bosco, mibuklat kaya ing pasbul ning kabanalan, a kinilala ning Iglesia Catolica anyang 1951. Ing pamitátag da reng salesiana ing pakibat neng pastoral Don Bosco king pamangailangan da reng dakal a kayanakan a talapagobra a mabibye king bunga ning Reboslusyong Industrial king Piedmont o Piamonete king Italia anyang kalabingsyam a dilanwa o siglu (''19th century''), at king parasan a iti, inampang nang Madre Mazzarello ing mitmu nang pagal ampong pamagpursigi.   

